{"tid":1890341,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"文在寅豪捐中國200萬副口罩 南韓1/3口罩廠卻停產","createTime":"2020-02-21T06:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T06:47:19.000Z","uid":75656,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"137fd41939f1405a935130845938f35335ad1a5f","tid":1890341,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:42:28.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國武漢肺炎自1月爆發迄今，疫情已蔓延全球多國，南韓總統文在寅先前決定捐給中國200萬副口罩，口罩廠卻爆料中方拒絕供應口罩原料，文在寅因此被南韓網友罵爆，而韓媒經揭露，韓國3分之1的口罩廠已經停產。<br />\n<br />\n根據南韓《MBN》報導，南韓政府自去年12月以來，一直在調查韓國123家口罩工廠的生產情況，如果工廠營運每天能夠運行8小時，那麼每間工廠每天至少能夠製作5萬個口罩，但目前已有口罩業者反映「根本無法經營」，雖然日以繼夜趕工，卻苦無原料。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，南韓口罩製造廠缺乏的是醫用口罩內的過濾層，韓國向來從中國進口大量口罩過濾層，而當中國自身缺乏此原料時，就停止該原料出口到其他國家，目前南韓國內公司所生產的口罩過濾層，僅足夠供應50％南韓口罩製造廠的需求量。<br />\n<br />\n儘管文在寅政府已經設立口罩每日生產量1000萬副的目標，但口罩原料的供應速度卻遠不及製造速度，南韓目前有3分之1的口罩製造廠中斷生產，且縫在口罩上的耳帶也即將面臨缺貨問題，南韓政府迫切需要採取應對措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3074872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3074872&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVNagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=950f5a0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3074872&h=e3afe54e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3074872</a>"},{"pid":"7203b83256a19cbf304a5377a60e7b4426a22f1b","tid":1890341,"uid":265881,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:43:31.000Z","msg":"左膠誤國 勇武興邦"},{"pid":"7967924823ec1f2dd2319c3f9cb8804424272e17","tid":1890341,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:44:33.000Z","msg":"［慶祝夠未］警 世 文！一齊打返起文宣戰線好嗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1890283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1890283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a8b517684b90043b8e4d929376c2ae011b09eedf","tid":1890341,"uid":15605,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:45:39.000Z","msg":"做完總統準備坐監"},{"pid":"5d0975b06c7d7d8e9c54dd62c04956dc754599b1","tid":1890341,"uid":166785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:48:07.000Z","msg":"韓國總統斬係要唔太正常先坐到上去"},{"pid":"6287d8f4f32e3464fa888fb1583c4502d5b832e0","tid":1890341,"uid":258696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:48:47.000Z","msg":"上一個就邪教<br />\n呢個就中共間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a45cc3cf12a10a9d02dcbf41768650734c0d839","tid":1890341,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"等韓國疫症爆完，睇嚟都準備下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec9c7c479703792c422491135ff17f1a8d18ecb","tid":1890341,"uid":256019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:17:21.000Z","msg":"支那狗特質係過橋抽板，無論政府同人民都一樣，所以對班畜牲仁慈即是對自己殘忍！只有滅絕成個族群，人類至有希望！"},{"pid":"a843112f556085fb1bc7b9babacf2f0d39649954","tid":1890341,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c837e0dd4c9c5d3aa2929bfce58be8564af917d","tid":1890341,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:27:32.000Z","msg":"奶共下場"},{"pid":"5ab5cf93b0968b8bc845f3a19f60cba389861d28","tid":1890341,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T06:27:38.000Z","msg":"泡菜國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我代表祖國感謝你們🙏🏼"},{"pid":"5043a39ce10efb54f99bef50ee4376091b839515","tid":1890341,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1ec9c7c479703792c422491135ff17f1a8d18ecb","tid":1890341,"uid":256019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:17:21.000Z","msg":"支那狗特質係過橋抽板，無論政府同人民都一樣，所以對班畜牲仁慈即是對自己殘忍！只有滅絕成